Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,KARAOKE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.54,0:00:13.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美(わしみ)）\Nドゥドゥドゥン ドゥンドゥン
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.12,0:00:14.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ドゥンドゥン ドゥンドゥン
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:17.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ドゥドゥドゥン ドゥンドゥン\Nドゥンドゥン ドゥンドゥン
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:21.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hakone Mountains are the steepest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:21.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）♪箱根(はこね)の山は 天下の険
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:21.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）ドゥドゥドゥン\Nドゥンドゥン ドゥン…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:21.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）ドゥドゥドゥン\Nドゥンドゥン ドゥン…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:24.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪函谷関(かんこくかん)も 物ならず
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:24.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）ドゥドゥドゥン\Nドゥンドゥン ドゥン…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:24.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Hangu Pass can't compare
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:26.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,They're ancient and tall\NWith a bottomless...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:26.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪万丈の山 千仞(せんじん)の…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:27.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:27.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）やめましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:31.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ やめないでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:31.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.29,0:00:35.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子(れつこ)が歌ってくれない今\N私たちが歌うしか ないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:35.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Retsuko is not around,\Nwe have no choice but to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:39.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to sing.\NI don't even know this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:39.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）歌う必要ないし\N第一知らないわよ そんな歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:41.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,名曲「箱根八里」を知らないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.75,0:00:42.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But 'Hakone Mountains' is a classic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:44.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,音楽の授業で習ったでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:44.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you learn it at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:47.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Back in my day, we didn't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:47.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）\N私たちの世代は習いませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:50.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,おいしい食べ物のあるお店\N行きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:50.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go grab some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.50,0:00:58.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,そうね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:00:58.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあ あそこ行こう\Nあのキッシュが おいしかったお店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:02.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,How about the place with the quiche?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:03.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）\Nゴリちゃん 好きよね あのお店
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.12,0:01:04.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like it there, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:07.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）\Nだって おいしいんだも～ん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.58,0:01:07.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's so yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.62,0:01:13.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:16.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,REQUEST RECEIVED
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:17.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,RAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:55.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:03.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）私は今 幸せです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:03.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:06.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The way he eats is messy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:06.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ちょっと\N食べ方がユニークだけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:09.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,子どもっぽくて かわいいから\N幸せです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's cute and childlike, so I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:13.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,人前で 平気で\N爪の においをかぐ しぐさも…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:13.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the way he sniffs his fingernails\Nin public...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,is quirky, so I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,かっこいいから幸せです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:21.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,すてきな彼氏と\Nこうして歩いているだけで―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:21.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Just walking together\Nwith my nice boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私は とても幸せなんです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:24.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel truly blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:38.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（坪根(つぼね)）ここーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:37.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:39.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ここと ここと―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:42.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,And here! And here!\NWhat do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:42.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ここと ここと ここと ここと\Nここと ここ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:44.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,全部 間違ってる！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:44.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:47.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いくら何でも ミスが多すぎるわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:47.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Way too many mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:49.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,こんなんじゃ\N安心して仕事 任せらんないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:49.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I trust you to do it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:51.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）すみません 直します
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.12,0:02:51.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry... I'll fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:56.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ハア… あなた 最近\Nおかしいんじゃないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:56.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been acting strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:58.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,前は もう少し 見どころあったわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:58.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You used to be better at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.58,0:03:01.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何か あったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:01.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:03.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,直します
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:03.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:18.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,TEA ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:22.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子の鼻歌）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:24.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田(だ)）なあ フェネ子(こ)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:25.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Hey, Fenneko.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:25.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Retsuko seeing someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:29.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田）\N烈子が つきあってる男って誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:31.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子の吹き出す音）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:33.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）な… 何の話？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:33.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:37.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,しらばっくれんなよ\N見てりゃ分かるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:37.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb... It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:39.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お前だったら\N何か情報 持ってんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You must know something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:40.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子の飲み込む音）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:45.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,多分 営業の れさすけって人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.29,0:03:45.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I think...\NIt's probably Resasuke from Sales.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:48.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私も ノーマークだった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:49.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:49.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何で フェネ子が謝るんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.50,0:03:52.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:56.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ハア…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:01.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,そいつ ぶん殴りてえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:01.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to punch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:21.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ～っ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:24.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!\NI've lost three kilos already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:24.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,見てください これ\N３キロも落ちてる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:25.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,どうしちゃったんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:28.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even know.\NIt means that yoga is working.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:28.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ヨガの成果が\N出始めたってことですかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:32.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not losing weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:32.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,それ 痩せたんじゃなくて…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:34.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）\Nやつれちゃったんじゃないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:39.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）思ったことを言うわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:39.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:42.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,今の烈子は\N幸せな彼女を演じてるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:42.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only pretending\Nto be a happy girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:46.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same thing at work -\Npretending to be a good employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:46.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,職場で 真面目な会社員を\N演じてたときと変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:49.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the real you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:49.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,そんなの 本当の烈子じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,そんなこと ないですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:52.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:56.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）私は別に\N演じたっていいと思うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:56.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with pretending.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:58.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ちょっと 鷲美！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:58.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Washimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:01.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）恋愛なんて\Nしたたかに演じたらいいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:01.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you have to act\Nin a relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:04.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you can make each other happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:04.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,それで お互い\N気分良くなれるんだもの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:06.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ただし―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:06.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:09.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,演じた自分を\N乗りこなすだけの度量が―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,only if you and your boyfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子と彼氏さんに\Nあるならって話よ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:12.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,have the capacity to keep up the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ないでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:14.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（店員）いらっしゃいませ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:25.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:28.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ごゆっくり ご覧くださ～い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:28.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take your time and look around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ かわいい！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:31.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:34.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.12,0:05:34.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,これ どう思います？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:38.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,かわいいですよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:39.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-It's quite cute, isn't it?\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:39.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（れさすけ）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:41.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）こっちは どう思います？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:41.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:45.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,こっちのほうが かわいい？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:46.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Is this one cuter?\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:46.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:50.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,でも やっぱり\N最初のほうがいいかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-I wonder if the first one is better.\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.12,0:05:52.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:55.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, both are pretty bland.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:55.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,やっぱり どっちも そんなに\Nかわいくないですかね？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:57.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,うん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:02.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,買わないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:02.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:04.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お手洗い 行ってきま～す
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:04.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Just going to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（れさすけ）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:06.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）いってえ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,RAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,After I count to ten,\NI'll be a happy girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）\N10数えたら 私は幸せな彼女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:30.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,After I count to ten,\NI'll be a happy girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:30.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,10数えたら 私は幸せな彼女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,10数えたら 私は幸せな彼女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:36.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,After I count to ten,\NI'll be a happy girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,10数えたら\N私は幸せな彼女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:36.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,10数えたら\N私は幸せな彼女…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:40.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,BAR
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:57.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田）うう…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:59.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:59.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,たーっ 畜生！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:01.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,うわっ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:12.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,だっせえな 俺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:21.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）くっそー！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:24.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Why now, of all times?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:24.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ったく この忙しいときによ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:28.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Director Ton! What should we do?\NYou have golf tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（小宮(こみや)）ト… トン部長！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:28.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,い… いかがいたしましょう？\Nあしたのゴルフは～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.75,0:07:30.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）バカ野郎 キャンセルだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.83,0:07:30.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Cancel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:34.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,四半期決算の締めが迫っている\Nこの時期―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:34.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The end of the quarter\Nis fast approaching,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:37.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,我らが経理部に欠員が出た
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:37.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,but we have staff shortages.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,１人目は ハイ田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:38.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Haida is out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.16,0:07:42.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,謎の高熱から 肺炎を併発し\N現在 入院中！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:42.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,He has developed pneumonia\Nand has been admitted to hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:43.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,全く情けない男です
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:43.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What a slacker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:45.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's Tsubone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:45.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）２人目は 坪根さん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:47.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,自宅で\N開かずの つくだ煮と格闘中―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:47.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,She tried to open one of her jars at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:50.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,She fractured her wrist\Nand is out of action!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:48.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,手首を粉砕骨折して\N戦線離脱！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:49.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（坪根のうめき声）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:49.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,手首を粉砕骨折して\N戦線離脱！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:49.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（坪根のうめき声）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:51.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,つくだ煮禁止令を出すべきです
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:51.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（坪根のうめき声）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:51.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,We should ban her jars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:52.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）３人目は カバ恵(え)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:55.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,And Kabae - she was accused of spying\Nand was detained by the authorities!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:55.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,スパイ容疑で 現在\N某国当局が身柄を拘束中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私たちの手に負えません
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:00.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,以上 ３人の穴を埋めるべく―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:04.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,To make up for their absence,\Nknuckle down and work as a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:04.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,残された者は 一丸となって\N事に当たってください
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:07.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いいや 欠員は４人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:07.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually... We're four workers down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:08.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,は？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,今のお前は\N使い物にならねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:18.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no good to us in this state.\NMake tea and keep out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:18.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,邪魔にならんよう\Nお茶くみでもしとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:30.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:30.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,次！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:33.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,次！ 次！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.50,0:08:36.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Next! Next! Keep them coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:35.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,次！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:36.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,うららららーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:39.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,やばくない？ あのスピード
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:39.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some crazy speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:43.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,パソコン使ってる私らより\N全然速いじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:43.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got computers,\Nbut he's still faster than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）おい フェネ子！\N（フェネ子）うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:44.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Fenneko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:48.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Check these invoices again!\NI can't approve them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.62,0:08:46.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,売り掛けの記載 もう一度 見直せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:48.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,これじゃ はんこ押せねえぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:51.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）は… はい\N（トン）うららららーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:50.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:53.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子）\N昭和のおっさん すげえな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:57.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-The analog generation sure is something!\N-Go back to square one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:57.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,御破算で願わせろやーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:00.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私 お茶いれてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.83,0:09:00.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:03.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,TEA ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:07.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（湯が沸く音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:17.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,コーヒーが飲みてえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:17.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ すぐ いれます
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'll make you some.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:23.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いや 自分で いれる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:22.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll make it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:27.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（蓋を開ける音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.37,0:09:29.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:34.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I can't help out\Nduring this busy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:34.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,こんなときに私\N何も お役に立てなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.04,0:09:39.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（すする音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:41.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）うー
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:44.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,１円たりとも ごまかさねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:44.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,No mistakes, down to the last yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:49.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,出てった金と入ってくる金を\N正確に勘定する
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:49.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Accurately counting the money\Nthat comes in and goes out -
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:52.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,それが経理の仕事だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:51.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,that's what accounting is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:56.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,１度ごまかしたやつは\N次も ごまかす
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:56.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Once someone messes up,\Nthey keep doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:10:01.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ごまかしが積み重なれば\N会社は病む 人も同じだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:10:01.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The more mistakes they make, the more\Nthe company and its people suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:05.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お前は いつまで\Nごまかし続けるつもりだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:05.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will you keep messing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:08.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,入るもんがないまま\N出るもんばかり―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:09.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep giving out more\Nthan you get back in return,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:12.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,多くなっちまったら あとは\Nゆっくりと痩せ細るだけだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,there won't be anything left in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:13.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,分かるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:13.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,分かります
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:16.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:20.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,でも 悪い人じゃないんです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a bad person...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:21.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,フン
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何の話だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:27.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,おっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:31.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you hate long lectures\Nfrom your shitty boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:31.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,クソ上司の長話は\N嫌いなんだったな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.29,0:10:34.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,うー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:42.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）私にも―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:42.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:45.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,仕事を下さい！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,give me something to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:49.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）なら 来い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:49.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:51.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,会社ってのはな―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:55.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Companies exist to make possible\Nwhat we can't do on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:55.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,１人じゃ できねえことを\Nやるためにあるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:19.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（いびき）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:33.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,KARAOKE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（店員）いらっしゃいませ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:37.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome... Party of three?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:37.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,３名様…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:40.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Party of two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:40.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,２名様ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:46.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ここ いつも使ってるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I come here all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.75,0:11:48.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,カラオケ 好きだったんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:48.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you liked karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:51.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:54.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,今まで うそ ついてました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:54.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been lying to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:58.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,れさすけさんが見ていた私は―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:12:00.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't shown you the real Retsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:00.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの私じゃないです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:02.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,SEND
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.29,0:12:09.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（デスメタルの音楽）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:30.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（デス烈子の叫び声）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:41.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for the truth about Retsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:41.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（デス烈子の歌声）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:44.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty-five years old, OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:47.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Scorpio, and my blood type is A!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I come to karaoke all the time\NAnd bring my mic and then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Slay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:56.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Heal the pain, in my secret place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:59.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Underneath the smile\NI'm metal till I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:02.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Underneath the smile\NI'm metal till I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:05.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Underneath the smile\NI'm metal to the bottom of my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:11.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's a place that would destroy you\N'Cause you're bland!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.08,0:13:16.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（拍手）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:20.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,すごく上手だね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:22.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really good.\NDon't mind me. Keep singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.50,0:13:22.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,僕は いいから\N続けて歌っていいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I put next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,次 何 入れる？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）終わった…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:32.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:34.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ドアが開く音）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are an awkward girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）ほんと不器用な子ね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Retsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,おかえり 烈子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:45.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ただいま
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:45.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:52.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ドアが開く音）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:05.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ただいま
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:13.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田）\N別に来なくていいって言ったのによ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to bother coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,元気そうだね\N（フェネ子）心配して 損した
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:16.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-You look fine.\N-I was worried over nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:20.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田）アハッ\N経理部 大変だったんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:20.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been tough in Accounting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:23.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）地獄だったよ\N（フェネ子）後で おごりな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.70,0:14:23.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-It was hell.\N-You owe us one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:27.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私 水 替えてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:27.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll change the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:31.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,じゃあね ごゆっくり～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:31.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,See you. Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:37.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田）烈子 大丈夫なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Retsuko, how are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:41.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,えっ 何が？\Nそれ こっちのセリフじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:41.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?\NI should be asking you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:45.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あの後 いろいろ聞いたからさ\Nほら―
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:44.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard some things...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:47.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,about the guy from Sales.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:47.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,営業部の…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:49.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:56.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,多分 そいつより俺のほうが\N烈子のこと 分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:56.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I know you better than he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:58.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,５年間 見てきたからな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I've known you for five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:00.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,絶対 分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:01.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:04.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,アハッ\Nと言いたいところだけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:07.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But the truth is that\NI probably don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:07.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとは多分\N何にも知らねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:12.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,俺が分かってんのは\N俺の頭ん中の烈子だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:12.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The Retsuko that I know\Nis the one in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:13.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:16.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,だから もっと ちゃんと\N知りたいっつうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:17.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why\NI would like to know you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.83,0:15:19.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あ… ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:21.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,言ってること 分かるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:21.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you catch my drift?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:22.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,分かるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:22.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:27.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,でも ちゃんと言ってくれないと\Nこっちも ちゃんと断れない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:27.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you don't ask properly,\NI can't give you a proper answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:32.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,そっか… そうだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:31.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:36.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あ… あのな…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.58,0:15:44.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）世界は いつだって―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:47.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Life doesn't always go the way you expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.12,0:15:47.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私たちの思いどおりになんて\Nなってくれない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:51.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,人生は 期待外れの連続で―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:53.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a series of disappointments\Nand misunderstandings...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:53.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,誤解や擦れ違いだらけだけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:54.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,KARAOKE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:15:57.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私たちは 不満や思いを\N吐き出しながら―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:59.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,...but we must work through our discontent\Nand move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:59.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,前に進むしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:02.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,進み続ければ―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:06.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,When we keep moving, we become\Na little stronger every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:06.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,昨日より\Nちょっとだけ強くなれるから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:22.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）腰掛け！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:24.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, short-timer! I told you to prepare\Nthe documents for the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.70,0:16:26.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,会議資料 作っとけって言ったろ！\Nさっさと持ってこい！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:27.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Bring them here now.\N-Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,はーい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:29.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（坪根）烈子さん つくだ煮開けて\N（烈子）はーい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:29.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Open this jar, Retsuko.\N-OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:31.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Now feed me.\N-Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:31.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（坪根）ほーら 食べさせて\N（烈子）はーい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:34.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Retsuko, pick up the phone already!\N-Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:34.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,烈子君 電話は\N３コール以内だと あれほど…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:34.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,はーい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:36.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（カバ恵）あのね\Nここだけの話なんだけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:37.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,This is only between us, OK?\NI did this and that became...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:37.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,アレが コレして\Nナニが コレして…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（角田(つのだ)）先輩 これ お願いしま～す\N（カバ恵）ブワ～ッてなって…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:39.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Retsuko, could you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:43.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,資料 お待たせしました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:43.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Your documents are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:45.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）フン
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:46.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:47.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）失礼しま～す
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ハッ 何だ こりゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:52.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,会議資料も作れねえのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:56.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that's done?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:58.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ぼーっと仕事してんじゃねえぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:17:01.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Always distracted!\NYou are the "pressure-free" generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:01.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ったく これだから ゆとりはよ～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:05.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,すみません\Nどこを直せばいいんでしょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:05.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize. What should I fix?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:08.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）あ？\Nそんなことも分からねえのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:08.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you don't even know...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You, slow-witted woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.66,0:17:10.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,目端の利かねえ女だな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:13.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,常識的に考えりゃ 分かんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.29,0:17:13.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's common knowledge, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:18.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いいか？\N書類の角を留めるときはな…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:18.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, when you staple documents...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:25.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,斜め45度で留めるんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:25.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to staple them\Nat a 45-degree angle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:34.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（デス烈子の叫び声）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:59.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:00.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Subtitle translation: John Haguewood
